    </p>
    <hr />
    <p class="text-xs text-center mt-2">
      Not on Pinterest yet? <a href="/register" class="font-semibold">Sign up</a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs text-cente mt-2">
      Are you a business? <a href="" class="font-semibold">Get started here!</a>
    </p>
